#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Strong mind bends the line."
msgstr "Kuchli aql chizig'ni egadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "A learning platform built for curious minds — where students grow through structured practice, mentorship from expert masters, and a community that pushes boundaries together."
msgstr "Qiziquvchan onglar uchun qurilgan ta'lim platformasi — o'quvchilar tizimli mashqlar, mutaxassis ustodlarning mentorlik va chegaralarni kengaytiruvchi jamoa orqali rivojlanadigan joy."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Start Practicing"
msgstr "Mashqni boshlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Free to Start"
msgstr "Bepul boshlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Clear Goal"
msgstr "Aniq maqsad"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Every Learner"
msgstr "Har bir o'quvchi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Bizning maqsadimiz"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Sharpening minds,"
msgstr "Onglarni charxlash,"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "one question at a time."
msgstr "har bir savol bilan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Prime Point was founded on a simple belief: the best way to build a strong mind is through deliberate, structured practice. We connect passionate learners with expert masters and give them the tools to grow — at their own pace, on their own terms."
msgstr "Prime Point oddiy bir e'tiqod asosida tashkil etilgan: kuchli ong qurishning eng yaxshi yo'li — maqsadli, tizimli mashq. Biz ishtiyoqli o'quvchilarni mutaxassis ustodlar bilan bog'laymiz va ularga o'sish uchun qurollar beramiz — o'z sur'atlarida, o'z shartlarida."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "We are not just a quiz app. We are a full learning ecosystem — from homework assignments to live discussion, from beginner practices to expert-level challenges."
msgstr "Biz shunchaki viktorina ilovasi emasmiz. Biz to'liq ta'lim ekotizimizmiz — uy vazifalaridan jonli muhokamagacha, boshlang'ich mashqlardan ekspert darajasidagi qiyinchiliklargacha."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Deliberate Practice"
msgstr "Maqsadli mashq"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Targeted, measurable improvement every session"
msgstr "Har bir mashg'ulotda aniq va o'lchovli taraqqiyot"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Expert Mentorship"
msgstr "Mutaxassis mentorlik"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Learn directly from masters in their field"
msgstr "O'z sohasidagi ustodlardan bevosita o'rganing"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Visible Progress"
msgstr "Ko'rinadigan taraqqiyot"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Track your rank from Novice to Grandmaster"
msgstr "Yangilikdan Grandmastergacha darajangizni kuzating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Community Learning"
msgstr "Jamoaviy ta'lim"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Discuss, debate, and grow alongside peers"
msgstr "Tengdoshlar bilan muhokama qiling va birgalikda rivojlaning"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "What We Offer"
msgstr "Nima taklif etamiz"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Everything you need to level up."
msgstr "Darajangizni oshirish uchun hamma narsa."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Hundreds of curated practice sessions across subjects and difficulty levels. Filter by topic, master, or level — and track your score every attempt."
msgstr "Turli fanlar va qiyinlik darajalari bo'yicha yuzlab tanlangan mashq sessiyalari. Mavzu, ustod yoki daraja bo'yicha filtrlang — va har bir urinishda natijangizni kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Homework System"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Masters assign targeted practice as homework to individual students or groups. Deadlines, auto-grading, and submission tracking built in."
msgstr "Ustodlar alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga uy vazifasi sifatida maqsadli mashqlar tayinlaydi. Muddatlar, avtomatik baholash va topshiriqlarni kuzatish o'rnatilgan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Master Profiles"
msgstr "Ustod profillari"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Follow experts in your field. Each master curates their own practice library and can guide their students through structured learning paths."
msgstr "Sohangizdagi mutaxassislarni kuzating. Har bir ustod o'zining mashqlar kutubxonasini boshqaradi va tizimli o'quv yo'llari orqali o'quvchilarini yo'naltiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Discussion Forum"
msgstr "Muhokama forumi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Engage with the community — ask questions, share insights, vote on answers, and learn from conversations that go beyond the practice sheet."
msgstr "Jamoa bilan muloqot qiling — savollar bering, fikrlar ulashing, javoblarga ovoz bering va mashq varag'idan tashqariga chiqadigan suhbatlardan o'rganing."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Rank System"
msgstr "Daraja tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Earn points through practice and climb from Novice to Grandmaster. Your rank reflects your dedication — and motivates you to keep going."
msgstr "Mashq orqali ball to'plang va Yangilikdan Grandmastergacha ko'tariling. Darajangiz fidoyiligingizni aks ettiradi — va davom etishga undaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Masters see exactly where each student struggles — question by question, choice by choice. Targeted feedback becomes effortless."
msgstr "Ustodlar har bir o'quvchining qayerda qiynalayotganini aniq ko'radi — savol savoldan, tanlov tanlovdan. Maqsadli fikr-mulohaza berish osonlashadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "Qanday ishlaydi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Simple steps. Real results."
msgstr "Oddiy qadamlar. Haqiqiy natijalar."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Create your account"
msgstr "Hisobingizni yarating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Sign up free in seconds. Build your student profile and choose your learning goals."
msgstr "Soniyalar ichida bepul ro'yxatdan o'ting. O'quvchi profilingizni yarating va o'quv maqsadlaringizni belgilang."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Follow a Master"
msgstr "Ustodni kuzating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Browse expert masters and follow the ones whose subjects align with your goals."
msgstr "Mutaxassis ustodlarni ko'rib chiqing va maqsadlaringizga mos keladiganlarini kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Practice & Submit"
msgstr "Mashq qiling va topshiring"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Take timed or open-ended practice sessions. Submit homework assigned by your masters."
msgstr "Vaqt chegaralangan yoki ochiq mashq sessiyalarini bajaring. Ustodlaringiz tomonidan berilgan uy vazifalarini topshiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Review & Grow"
msgstr "Tahlil qiling va rivojlaning"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "See detailed feedback on every answer. Improve your weak points. Rise through the ranks."
msgstr "Har bir javob uchun batafsil fikr-mulohaza ko'ring. Zaif tomonlaringizni yaxshilang. Darajangizni oshiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "The Team"
msgstr "Jamoa"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
msgid "Built by people who care about learning."
msgstr "O'rganishga g'amxo'r odamlar tomonidan qurilgan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html
