#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Approved Masters have a full suite of teaching and management tools at their disposal."
msgstr "Tasdiqlangan Ustodlarda o'qitish va boshqarish uchun to'liq vositalar to'plami mavjud."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Create Practices"
msgstr "Mashqlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Build multiple-choice question sets with difficulty levels (easy / medium / hard), time limits, pass scores, and max attempt caps."
msgstr "Qiyinlik darajasi (oson / o'rta / qiyin), vaqt chegarasi, o'tish bali va maksimal urinishlar bilan test savollari to'plamlari tuzing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Manage Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilarni boshqarish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "View everyone who follows you. Remove students from your roster and organise them into named groups for bulk operations."
msgstr "Sizi kuzatayotgan barcha kishilarni ko'ring. O'quvchilarni ro'yxatdan o'chiring va ommaviy amallar uchun ularni nomlangan guruhlarga joylashtiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Create Groups"
msgstr "Guruhlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Group students by class, level, or any criteria. Assign homework to a whole group with a single action instead of individually."
msgstr "O'quvchilarni sinf, daraja yoki boshqa mezonlar bo'yicha guruhlang. Har biri alohida o'rniga bitta amal bilan butun guruhga uy vazifasi tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Assign Homework"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tayinlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Link any practice to individual students or groups, add notes, and set an optional deadline. Track status — Pending, Submitted, or Graded."
msgstr "Har qanday mashqni alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga bog'lang, izoh qo'shing va ixtiyoriy muddat belgilang. Holat — Kutilmoqda, Topshirilgan yoki Baholangan."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
