#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Publish rich-text articles with a category, thumbnail, and linked practices. Students can like or dislike your tutorials."
msgstr "Kategoriya, eskiz va bog'langan mashqlar bilan boy matnli maqolalar chop eting. O'quvchilar darsliklaringizni yoqtirishi yoki yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Run Classrooms"
msgstr "Darsxonalarni yuritish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Create private classrooms with structured lessons. Attach practices, homework, and tutorials to each lesson. Host a classroom-level discussion."
msgstr "Tuzilgan darslar bilan xususiy darsxonalar yarating. Har bir darsga mashqlar, uy vazifalari va darsliklarni biriktiring. Darsxona darajasida muhokama o'tkazing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Generate Certificates"
msgstr "Sertifikatlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Issue printable certificates to your students directly from your Master profile page — no third-party tool needed."
msgstr "O'quvchilaringizga Ustod profili sahifangizdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri chop etiladigan sertifikatlar bering — uchinchi tomon vositasi shart emas."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "For Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilar uchun"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Student Guide"
msgstr "O'quvchi qo'llanmasi"

