msgstr "Bajarildi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Feature Guide"
msgstr "Xususiyatlar bo'yicha qo'llanma"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Platform Features"
msgstr "Platforma xususiyatlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Practice System"
msgstr "Mashqlar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Practices are the core of Prime Point. Each practice is a set of multiple-choice questions created by a master. Masters configure exactly how students experience each practice."
msgstr "Mashqlar Prime Pointning asosi. Har bir mashq ustod tomonidan yaratilgan ko'p tanlovli savollar to'plami. Ustodlar o'quvchilar har bir mashqni qanday boshdan kechirishini aniq sozlaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Three difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, Hard."
msgstr "Uchta qiyinlik darajasi: Oson, O'rta, Qiyin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Optional time limit — the timer counts down and auto-submits when it expires."
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy vaqt chegarasi — taymer orqaga hisoblaydi va muddati tugaganda avtomatik topshiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Pass score threshold — you must reach this percentage to pass."
msgstr "O'tish bali chegarasi — o'tish uchun ushbu foizga yetishingiz kerak."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Max attempts cap — masters can limit how many times a student can retry."
msgstr "Maksimal urinishlar chegarasi — ustodlar o'quvchi necha marta qayta urinishini cheklashi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Show-answers-after option — correct answers are revealed once the attempt is completed."
msgstr "To'g'ri javoblarni ko'rsatish opsiyasi — urinish tugagandan so'ng to'g'ri javoblar ochiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Free and available-for-all flags — masters can open a practice to the entire platform."
msgstr "Bepul va hammaga ochiq bayroqlar — ustodlar mashqni butun platforma uchun ochaoladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Practice Metadata"
msgstr "Mashq ma'lumotlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Level"
msgstr "Daraja"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Max Attempts"
msgstr "Maks. urinishlar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Masters link a practice to a homework assignment and push it directly to students or groups. Students complete the linked practice to submit the homework."
msgstr "Ustodlar mashqni uy vazifasiga bog'laydi va to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga yuboradi. O'quvchilar uy vazifasini topshirish uchun bog'langan mashqni bajaradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Create homework: give it a title, optional notes, a linked practice, and an optional due date."
msgstr "Uy vazifasini yarating: sarlavha, ixtiyoriy izoh, bog'langan mashq va ixtiyoriy topshirish muddatini kiriting."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Assign to individual students or to an entire group in one step."
msgstr "Bir qadamda alohida o'quvchilarga yoki butun guruhga tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Student completes the practice → homework status moves to Submitted automatically."
msgstr "O'quvchi mashqni bajaradi → uy vazifasi holati avtomatik ravishda Topshirilgan'ga o'tadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Master grades the submission and can leave written feedback."
msgstr "Ustod topshiriqni baholaydi va yozma fikr bildirishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Track per-student status from the homework detail view."
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tafsilotlari ko'rinishidan har bir o'quvchi holatini kuzating."

