msgstr "Guruh: Ilg'or sinf"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "students"
msgstr "o'quvchi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Practice: Grammar Test 3"
msgstr "Mashq: Grammatika testi 3"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Due date"
msgstr "Topshirish muddati"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Tutorial System"
msgstr "Darsliklar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Tutorials are long-form rich-text articles written by masters. They can include images, formatted text, and links to related practices — turning a lesson into an interactive experience."
msgstr "Darsliklar — ustodlar tomonidan yozilgan boy matnli uzun maqolalar. Ular rasmlar, formatlangan matn va tegishli mashqlarga havolalarni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin — darsni interaktiv tajribaga aylantiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Categories: Mathematics, Korean, Programming, English, Other."
msgstr "Kategoriyalar: Matematika, Koreys, Dasturlash, Ingliz, Boshqa."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Read time is estimated automatically from the word count."
msgstr "O'qish vaqti so'zlar sonidan avtomatik hisoblanadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Students can like or dislike a tutorial to give the author feedback."
msgstr "O'quvchilar muallifga fikr bildirish uchun darslikni yoqtirishi yoki yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Link any number of practices to a tutorial so students can test themselves immediately."
msgstr "O'quvchilar darhol o'zlarini sinab ko'rishi uchun darslikka istalgan miqdordagi mashqlarni bog'lang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "View count is tracked so masters can see which tutorials are most popular."
msgstr "Ko'rishlar soni kuzatiladi, shuning uchun ustodlar qaysi darsliklar mashhurligini ko'rishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Tutorial Card"
msgstr "Darslik kartasi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Programming"
msgstr "Dasturlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Classroom System"
msgstr "Darsxona tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Classrooms are private learning spaces managed by a master. They contain structured lessons, and only enrolled students can access the content."
msgstr "Darsxonalar — ustod tomonidan boshqariladigan xususiy ta'lim makonlari. Ular tuzilgan darslarni o'z ichiga oladi va faqat ro'yxatdan o'tgan o'quvchilar kontentga kira oladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Add students individually or import a whole group at once."
msgstr "O'quvchilarni alohida qo'shing yoki butun guruhni bir vaqtda import qiling."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Each classroom has ordered lessons with a status: Not Started, Ongoing, or Finished."
msgstr "Har bir darsxonada tartibli darslar mavjud: Boshlanmagan, Davom etmoqda yoki Tugallangan."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Attach practices, homework assignments, and tutorials to any lesson."
msgstr "Har qanday darsga mashqlar, uy vazifalari va darsliklarni biriktiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Upload lesson notes (PDFs, slides) that students can download per lesson."
msgstr "O'quvchilar har bir dars uchun yuklab olishi mumkin bo'lgan dars eslatmalarini (PDF, slaydlar) yuklang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Each classroom has its own discussion board for class-specific questions."
msgstr "Har bir darsxonada sinf-xususiy savollar uchun o'zining muhokama doskasi mavjud."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Lesson Structure"
msgstr "Dars tuzilishi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Lesson 1: Introduction"
msgstr "1-dars: Kirish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Tugallangan"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Lesson 2: Core Concepts"
msgstr "2-dars: Asosiy tushunchalar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Ongoing"
msgstr "Davom etmoqda"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Lesson 3: Practice Session"
msgstr "3-dars: Mashq sessiyasi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Not Started"
msgstr "Boshlanmagan"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "The platform-wide discussion forum lets anyone ask questions, share insights, or start a conversation. The best answers rise to the top through community voting."
msgstr "Platformadagi muhokama forumi har kimga savol berish, fikr ulashish yoki suhbat boshlash imkonini beradi. Eng yaxshi javoblar jamoat ovoz berishi orqali yuqoriga ko'tariladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Threads are organised by category — find the right section quickly."
msgstr "Mavzular kategoriya bo'yicha tartiblanadi — kerakli bo'limni tez toping."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Announcements and pinned threads stay at the top of their category."
msgstr "E'lonlar va mahkamlangan mavzular o'z kategoriyasining yuqorisida qoladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Upvote helpful threads and replies — downvote off-topic ones."
msgstr "Foydali mavzular va javoblarga ovoz bering — mavzuga mos kelmaydiganlarga salbiy ovoz bering."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Thread authors can mark one reply as the accepted answer."
msgstr "Mavzu mualliflari bitta javobni qabul qilingan javob sifatida belgilashi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Sort by Latest, Most Votes, Recent Activity, or Unanswered."
msgstr "Eng yangi, Ko'p ovozli, So'nggi faollik yoki Javobsiz bo'yicha tartiblash."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Thread Example"
msgstr "Mavzu namunasi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "How do I improve my score?"
msgstr "Balimni qanday yaxshilayman?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "replies"
msgstr "javob"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Best answer accepted"
msgstr "Eng yaxshi javob qabul qilindi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Progression"
msgstr "Rivojlanish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Your rank is calculated from the total points earned across all completed practices. The higher your score on each attempt, the more points you receive."
msgstr "Darajangiz barcha bajarilgan mashqlar bo'yicha to'plangan umumiy ballar asosida hisoblanadi. Har bir urinishdagi balingiz qanchalik yuqori bo'lsa, shunchalik ko'proq ball olasiz."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Points: 0 – 49"
msgstr "Ball: 0 – 49"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Just getting started. Every journey begins here."
msgstr "Endigina boshlanmoqda. Har qanday yo'l shu yerdan boshlanadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Points: 50 – 149"
msgstr "Ball: 50 – 149"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Building knowledge and consistent study habits."
msgstr "Bilim va muntazam o'qish odatlarini shakllantirish."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Points: 150 – 299"
msgstr "Ball: 150 – 299"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Deep understanding across multiple subjects."
msgstr "Bir nechta fanda chuqur tushuncha."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Points: 300+"
msgstr "Ball: 300+"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "The highest rank. Mastery of the platform's hardest challenges."
msgstr "Eng yuqori daraja. Platformaning eng qiyin sinovlarini egallash."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "Ko'p so'raladigan savollar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Ko'p so'raladigan savollar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Is Prime Point free?"
msgstr "Prime Point bepulmi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Yes. Creating an account, following masters, taking practices, and participating in discussions is completely free. Some practices may be marked as free by the master; others may be restricted to enrolled students only."
msgstr "Ha. Hisob yaratish, ustodlarga obuna bo'lish, mashqlar topshirish va muhokamada ishtirok etish mutlaqo bepul. Ba'zi mashqlar ustod tomonidan bepul deb belgilanishi mumkin; boshqalari faqat ro'yxatdan o'tgan o'quvchilar uchun cheklanishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "How do I become a Master?"
msgstr "Qanday qilib Ustod bo'laman?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Visit the Masters page and click 'Become a Master'. Complete the short application form with your name, subject area, and a brief description. An administrator will review and approve your application. Once approved, all master tools are unlocked immediately."
msgstr "Ustodlar sahifasiga o'ting va 'Ustod bo'lish' tugmasini bosing. Ismingiz, fan sohaniz va qisqa tavsif bilan qisqa ariza shaklini to'ldiring. Administrator arizangizni ko'rib chiqadi va tasdiqlaydi. Tasdiqlanganidan so'ng barcha ustod vositalari darhol ochiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "How do I follow a Master?"
msgstr "Ustodga qanday obuna bo'laman?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Go to your Profile page and scroll to the Masters section. Use the multi-select to add any masters you want to follow, then save your profile. You can add or remove masters at any time the same way."
msgstr "Profil sahifangizga o'ting va Ustodlar bo'limiga o'ting. Kuzatmoqchi bo'lgan ustodlarni qo'shish uchun ko'p tanlovdan foydalaning, so'ng profilingizni saqlang. Xuddi shu tarzda istalgan vaqt ustodlarni qo'shish yoki o'chirish mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "How are points earned?"
msgstr "Ballar qanday to'planadi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Each time you complete a practice, points are added to your student profile based on your score. Higher scores give more points. Points accumulate across all practices and determine your rank on the platform."
msgstr "Har safar mashqni bajarganingizda, ballaringizga qarab o'quvchi profilingizga ball qo'shiladi. Yuqori ball ko'proq ball beradi. Ballar barcha mashqlar bo'yicha to'planadi va platformadagi darajangizni belgilaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "What happens if I exceed the maximum attempts on a practice?"
msgstr "Mashqdagi maksimal urinishlardan oshib ketsam nima bo'ladi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Once you reach the maximum attempts set by the master, the Start button is disabled and you will see a message indicating you have used all your attempts. Contact your master if you need an additional attempt."
msgstr "Ustod tomonidan belgilangan maksimal urinishlarga yetganingizdan so'ng, Boshlash tugmasi o'chiriladi va barcha urinishlaringizni ishlatganligi haqida xabar ko'rasiz. Qo'shimcha urinish kerak bo'lsa, ustodingizga murojaat qiling."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Can I enroll in multiple classrooms?"
msgstr "Bir nechta darsxonaga yozilish mumkinmi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Yes. A master can add you to as many classrooms as they manage. Each classroom is independent with its own lessons, content, and discussion board."
msgstr "Ha. Ustod sizni boshqaradigan darsxonalarning istalganiga qo'shishi mumkin. Har bir darsxona o'z darslari, kontenti va muhokama doskasi bilan mustaqil."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Can a master see my homework submissions and scores?"
msgstr "Ustod uy vazifasini topshirishlarimni va ballarimni ko'ra oladimi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Yes. When a master assigns homework, they can view each student's submission status, score, and any written feedback they leave. This lets masters track progress and provide personalised guidance."
msgstr "Ha. Ustod uy vazifasini tayinlaganida, har bir o'quvchining topshirish holati, bali va qoldirgan yozma fikrlarini ko'rishi mumkin. Bu ustodlarga rivojlanishni kuzatish va shaxsiylashtirilgan yo'riqnoma berish imkonini beradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "What tutorial categories are available?"
msgstr "Qanday darslik kategoriyalari mavjud?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Tutorials are organised into five categories: Mathematics, Korean, Programming, English, and Other. Masters choose the best matching category when publishing a tutorial."
msgstr "Darsliklar beshta kategoriyaga bo'lingan: Matematika, Koreys, Dasturlash, Ingliz va Boshqa. Ustodlar darslik chop etishda eng mos kategoriyani tanlaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "Boshlashga tayyormisiz?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html
msgid "Join Prime Point today — it is free for students and educators alike."
msgstr "Bugun Prime Pointga qo'shiling — o'quvchilar va o'qituvchilar uchun bepul."

